Motormaster looks around the base, this was no doubt using up the bases
power, Wildrider better have a good reason for this. "Decepticons, scatter,
were probably under attack, he quickly rushes out, the same dirrection
Squawktalk had gone, and sees Condor escaping, "Slag it all, get back in
yer cell" Motormaster shouts, as he levels his Cyclone gun towards Condor.
"Decepticons, aprehend the Maximal, at all costs".
